Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.43,0:00:05.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, on top of me is a flood,\Nand below me is a big fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.97,0:00:07.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.70,0:00:09.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A hot spring!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.26,0:00:10.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.89,0:00:12.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't the answer be a hot tub?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.69,0:00:14.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't heat up a hot spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.69,0:00:17.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, but isn't not necessarily wrong, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.19,0:00:22.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Most hot springs are heated up by\Nconstantly burning magma, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.42,0:00:25.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, that's true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.12,0:00:28.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this about, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.75,0:00:31.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With you taking us to the hot springs, Professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.67,0:00:33.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going there to do some repairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.83,0:00:40.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's this inn owner who really liked this\Ninvention of mine and bought a large quantity.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.71,0:00:43.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've heard the guests love it a lot too, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.90,0:00:46.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Recently is seems to keep breaking down.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.13,0:00:47.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did you make?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.91,0:00:53.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it something like a chair that simulates the effect\Nand feel of being in a hot spring just by sitting in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.46,0:00:54.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.72,0:00:57.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it were something like that, we wouldn't need hot springs.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.66,0:00:59.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, just look forward to seeing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.09,0:01:05.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's probably some worthless invention as always...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.90,0:01:28.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we continue lamenting the passing seasons...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.69,0:01:30.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll be unable to confront the mysteries of cases!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.84,0:01:32.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An open-air bath atop a lake...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.49,0:01:34.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And a sealed-room mystery before dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.52,0:01:36.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.19,0:01:37.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.99,0:01:40.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.88,0:03:16.41,Signs,,0,0,0,,Hakone Hot Springs Kobou Inn
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.00,0:03:32.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The current water temperature is 42.3Â°C.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.17,0:03:38.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The total sulfur content per kilogram of water is 25.7 milligrams.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.20,0:03:40.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This hot spring is a sulfur spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.15,0:03:43.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.52,0:03:48.75,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,It is effective for skin diseases, arteriosclerosis,\Nskin enhancement, rheumatism...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.77,0:03:54.04,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Nervous disorders, and sensitivity to cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.74,0:03:48.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's that doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.24,0:03:51.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's Ishikawa Goemon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.53,0:03:54.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If someone is to speak of Japanese\Nbathtubs, it has to be Ishikawa Goemon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.62,0:03:57.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wasn't he executed by being boiled in an iron pot?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.62,0:04:00.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When ingested, it may also have medicinal effects...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.63,0:04:02.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A... gainst...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.96,0:04:04.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Diabetes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.42,0:04:05.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gout...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.68,0:04:08.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cons...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.15,0:04:09.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ti...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.10,0:04:20.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like Goemon is totally steamed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.31,0:04:23.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems the moving parts are worn and\Nwater seeped into the inner workings.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.02,0:04:26.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you fix them overnight?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.23,0:04:28.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.28,0:04:30.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've brought all the parts with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.57,0:04:32.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll make them sturdier this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.70,0:04:33.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.91,0:04:35.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You still haven't finished cleaning?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.91,0:04:37.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it already past 1:00?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.50,0:04:39.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please wait ten more minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.25,0:04:41.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.46,0:04:45.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was planning to try each of the five spas here before filming starts!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.59,0:04:49.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, you could try them after filming as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.71,0:04:50.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.92,0:04:54.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Might you be the actress Natori Mishio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.80,0:04:56.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.81,0:04:58.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.01,0:05:01.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You played the role of the first generation\NKamen Yaiba's love interest, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.10,0:05:04.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were very cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.27,0:05:05.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And so nice to everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.20,0:05:11.16,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Natori Mishio (28)\NActress
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.31,0:05:11.16,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Seems I did play such a ridiculous role once, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.36,0:05:15.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that was a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.78,0:05:17.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you please not remind me of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.29,0:05:20.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She seems different from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.41,0:05:22.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She always used to be smiling...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.41,0:05:23.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is she tsundere?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.17,0:05:26.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.75,0:05:30.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's just irritated right now because she's focused on her role.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.34,0:05:35.39,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Even I, as a manager, find it hard to talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.85,0:05:35.39,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Tanzawa Junsaku (34)\NMishio's Manager
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.68,0:05:38.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By "her role", do you mean you're filming a drama or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.76,0:05:41.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She did say something about filming a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.06,0:05:43.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.52,0:05:45.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a movie to be released next year...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.11,0:05:50.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The supreme masterpiece of the Blood Spray Hitman series...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.56,0:05:52.87,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Titled Scarlet Wellspring
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.88,0:05:56.14,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Of course, the scriptwriter is yours truly, Tetsuyama Ganji.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.87,0:05:56.87,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\be5\fad(210,0)}Tetsuyama Ganji (67)\NScriptwriter
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.24,0:06:00.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think you runts know of me, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.95,0:06:03.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know, I know of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.87,0:06:07.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you're finally going to remake Scarlet Wellspring?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.79,0:06:09.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.00,0:06:11.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Blood Spray Hitman"...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.09,0:06:12.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A story about a professional killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.38,0:06:16.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For some reason, he was hired to do a job in a spa town.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.34,0:06:19.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As a result, the steam became saturated\Nwith blood, giving him his namesake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.18,0:06:24.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The series is that old man's debut work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.68,0:06:28.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The story of the hitman protagonist is separated\Ninto the Youth part from when he was young...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.23,0:06:31.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the Old-Age part from when he had gotten on in years.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.23,0:06:35.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Scarlet Wellspring is the only\Ntitle that belongs to the Midlife part.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.11,0:06:42.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I remember the story, the main character\Nquit being a hitman due to a certain incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.41,0:06:47.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But for the sake of the hot spring inn hostess,\Nhe decided to start helping her kill for free...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.04,0:06:50.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And set up a perfect sealed-room murder, or something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.34,0:06:58.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the Midlife part that is Scarlet Wellspring was\Nfilmed just once, a long time ago in black and white.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.51,0:07:02.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They haven't been able to remake it\Nsince they couldn't find a suitable actor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.35,0:07:09.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Despite the fact that the Youth and Old-Age parts have\Nbeen remade many times using various actors and directors.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.15,0:07:11.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And as such...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.53,0:07:18.25,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Yours truly, the ideal embodiment of\Nthe middle-aged hitman, has appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.03,0:07:18.25,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Teradou Unpei (33)\NActor
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.66,0:07:21.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Teradou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, you've come too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.66,0:07:22.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.62,0:07:25.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd heard the heroine hostess had already arrived...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.87,0:07:28.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I ditched my manager and flew here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.17,0:07:31.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before the film staff arrives tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.92,0:07:35.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was thinking I could get to know\Nthe beautiful hostess a little better...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.34,0:07:41.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop doing whatever you like to my actress!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.18,0:07:48.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, the role you're playing is that of a grief-stricken\Nmiddle-aged man, exhausted by the business of killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.31,0:07:52.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not that of a skirt-chasing pervert with undisguised lust, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.36,0:07:54.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.65,0:08:00.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a completely different story from the\Npompous showoff you played in the Youth part!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.40,0:08:03.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.12,0:08:05.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd seen your face somewhere before...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.74,0:08:08.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're that actor, Tanzawa Junsaku{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.58,0:08:10.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.75,0:08:13.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were the best hitman!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.75,0:08:16.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would've been nice if you played the Midlife part too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.84,0:08:17.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.42,0:08:19.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.42,0:08:22.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've taken a break from acting due to various reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.89,0:08:26.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you could be dragged back into acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.26,0:08:31.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Given that the cast could be completely changed\Non a whim by our great scriptwriter here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.81,0:08:32.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.73,0:08:33.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.65,0:08:38.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I already have two or three actors in mind as your substitute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.28,0:08:40.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Depending on your performance, a change could occur.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.57,0:08:45.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, that goes for you as well, Natori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.87,0:08:46.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I suppose so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.12,0:08:49.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, do take a nice bath in the spa...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.96,0:08:53.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cleanse your body and reliably play the part of a hostess for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.58,0:08:57.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since there will be wet scenes in the film.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.17,0:09:00.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.22,0:09:01.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A "wet scene"...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.38,0:09:04.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that when you take a bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.43,0:09:05.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.89,0:09:07.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because the body gets all wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.97,0:09:10.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, let's just leave it at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.69,0:09:18.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with that man's leg?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.86,0:09:22.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He injured his tendon a number of years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.16,0:09:28.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As a result, he's been walking like that ever\Nsince, according to one documentary on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.49,0:09:30.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, since we came all this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.66,0:09:33.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't we try this hot spring inn's specialty...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.25,0:09:35.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The laketop outdoor spa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.96,0:09:37.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.63,0:09:43.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As the name implies, it's an open-air bath\Nmade on top of a lake with a great view.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.09,0:09:46.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This place and Tottori's Hawai Hot\NSpring are the only ones known to exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.55,0:09:48.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.14,0:09:53.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, why is the women's bath larger?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.52,0:09:57.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They'll switch the men's and women's\Nbaths after they finish cleaning at noon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.69,0:09:58.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:09:59.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.94,0:10:01.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.95,0:10:08.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like it's really crowded.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.29,0:10:11.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The women's bath is crowded as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.50,0:10:13.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.83,0:10:15.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's make it the first thing we do in the morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.58,0:10:19.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the morning the men's side will be the larger one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.04,0:10:22.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Soaking in hot water while gazing at\Nthe rising sun would be nice too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.84,0:10:23.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.34,0:10:24.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.05,0:10:29.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're atop the lake exposed to the wind, no wonder it's so cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.14,0:10:32.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go back to our room now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.94,0:10:39.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you've finally come around, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.73,0:10:42.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the laketop outdoor spa...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.69,0:10:44.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With the morning sun shining...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.78,0:10:47.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wonderful, wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.45,0:10:49.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The man in the lead role?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.12,0:10:52.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he doesn't please you, we can make a switch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.55,0:11:08.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Mishio?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.39,0:11:11.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It sounded like something shattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.10,0:11:13.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.60,0:11:15.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.85,0:11:16.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.24,0:11:33.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.49,0:11:36.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the manager from yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.50,0:11:40.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're up early.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.88,0:11:42.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's only 4:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.92,0:11:44.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got a problem, runt?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.60,0:11:53.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm back...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.01,0:11:55.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're late, Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.93,0:11:58.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How long can it take you to just buy some drinks?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.19,0:12:01.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because you had me go and buy them all by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.98,0:12:03.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not to mention asking for all kinds of things!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.27,0:12:06.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's your fault for sucking at rock-paper-scissors.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.69,0:12:09.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That old man with the pipe from yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.57,0:12:10.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's going to the spa so early!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.03,0:12:13.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.20,0:12:14.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's crossing the bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.99,0:12:18.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It doesn't open until 5:00 AM, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.41,0:12:20.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's currently 4:43.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.67,0:12:22.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that cheating!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.75,0:12:24.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We should go too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.80,0:12:29.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll let the professor sleep in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.59,0:12:30.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.47,0:12:32.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was up late making repairs after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.64,0:12:38.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How come that old man's allowed in, but we aren't?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.93,0:12:42.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, that sensei is an honored guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.02,0:12:43.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So we made a special exception for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.73,0:12:45.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.02,0:12:47.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's only about ten minutes until 5:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.07,0:12:49.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.53,0:12:50.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I suppose it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.61,0:12:55.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's dangerous to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.58,0:13:02.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I haven't taken a bath in three days!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.00,0:13:07.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You need to thoroughly wash yourself before you get in the spa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.34,0:13:08.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll wash myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.51,0:13:14.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That old man's clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.09,0:13:15.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't see them here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.24,0:13:31.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Ayumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.53,0:13:33.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.82,0:13:35.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.93,0:13:40.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.79,0:13:43.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this old man in the women's bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.25,0:13:46.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.79,0:13:49.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, this was a murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.21,0:13:51.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Furthermore...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.55,0:13:54.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A sealed-room murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.14,0:14:05.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.56,0:14:06.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.11,0:14:10.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I came to try the laketop outdoor spa...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.07,0:14:12.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But those kids wouldn't let me pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.49,0:14:15.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like I said, we can't let anyone inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.45,0:14:17.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan said so!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.87,0:14:18.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.49,0:14:21.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that person dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.66,0:14:22.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.08,0:14:24.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Already stopped breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.29,0:14:25.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.29,0:14:26.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.50,0:14:29.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You contacted the police already, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.59,0:14:30.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.13,0:14:34.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tetsuyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.97,0:14:35.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why is sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.59,0:14:37.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.18,0:14:38.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't touch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.35,0:14:39.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tetsuyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.27,0:14:48.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The cause of death is acute subdural hematoma due\Nto blunt force trauma in addition to cerebral contusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.15,0:14:51.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The estimated time of death is about 5:00 this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.48,0:14:54.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Traces of lather are on the bottom of the vic's feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.53,0:14:57.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The tiles beneath his feet also have lather residues.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.12,0:15:03.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, seeing that the soap flew\Nover there across from his feet...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.00,0:15:09.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems that while getting out of the bath, he\Naccidentally stepped on the soap, slipped, and fell...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.54,0:15:13.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thus hitting his head on the rocks around the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.17,0:15:15.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt that this was an accidental death.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.05,0:15:18.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, isn't it strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.44,0:15:20.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the women's bath, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.18,0:15:21.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Again with this brat, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.64,0:15:25.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I also thought that was strange, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.68,0:15:29.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When this old man arrived at this outdoor\Nspa, it was only a little past 4:30 AM.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.65,0:15:34.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was still dark outside, so he likely\Nmistook the women's bath for the men's.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.53,0:15:38.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, we also came here right after that man did...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.62,0:15:43.42,Signs,,0,0,0,,å¥³: Women
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.62,0:15:43.42,Signs,,0,0,0,,ç·: Men
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.32,0:15:43.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And we could clearly see the characters for\Nmen and women on the entrance curtains!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.24,0:15:47.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, didn't you meet them too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.08,0:15:50.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The two employees at the entrance to\Nthe bridge from the main building!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.84,0:15:53.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those two told me this:
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.96,0:15:56.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before the kids came, the person who went through the entrance...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.22,0:16:00.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was solely this old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.01,0:16:05.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you were the next to arrive after\Nthe old man and discovered his body...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.22,0:16:07.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then this was an accident no matter how you consider, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.60,0:16:09.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But just look there...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.60,0:16:11.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the old man's collar bone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.69,0:16:14.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a pool of water.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.73,0:16:17.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, his belly button too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.15,0:16:22.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he fell hard enough to die from hitting his head...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.74,0:16:25.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then any water on his body should've been knocked off, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.66,0:16:26.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.33,0:16:34.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps someone poured water on the old man\Nafter he fell in order to wash something off?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.59,0:16:37.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by wash off...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.51,0:16:39.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, the blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.63,0:16:44.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The unnatural blood spray that ended up on his\Nshoulders and back when he was initally struck...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.81,0:16:49.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After using the spa's rock to deliver a final\Nblow to his head, the culprit washed it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.35,0:16:51.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In order to make it look like an accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.31,0:16:53.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.86,0:17:01.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you found the body, there wasn't\Nanyone here expect for you kids, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.20,0:17:02.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.11,0:17:05.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There also weren't any loud noises\Nof someone jumping into the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.49,0:17:09.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means this laketop outdoor spa...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.25,0:17:13.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was a completely sealed room!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.46,0:17:16.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's an impossible crime, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.50,0:17:20.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, unless we can solve that mystery first...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.01,0:17:21.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.47,0:17:25.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Brats shouldn't spout off pretending to be detectives!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.39,0:17:29.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, call the forensics back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.52,0:17:32.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're going to thoroughly investigate again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.02,0:17:33.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.77,0:17:34.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.90,0:17:37.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.78,0:17:39.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.07,0:17:40.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You saw that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.65,0:17:41.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saw what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.57,0:17:44.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know, "that".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.66,0:17:45.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"That".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.41,0:17:47.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumi screamed really loud, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.58,0:17:48.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.99,0:17:50.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you really...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.04,0:17:51.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did see that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.25,0:17:52.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure did.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.96,0:17:55.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's quite natural when going to the bath...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.67,0:17:57.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To be totally naked and exposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.00,0:18:00.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Totally naked!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.46,0:18:01.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exposed!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.67,0:18:03.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You littleâ!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.18,0:18:04.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} is a dumb dumb dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.47,0:18:08.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Both of you saw that too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.18,0:18:09.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The old man's corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.85,0:18:12.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What were you guys talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.94,0:18:13.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.85,0:18:16.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About that old man's body, we saw it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.90,0:18:19.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We peeked before the police got here...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.73,0:18:21.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could that be possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.53,0:18:23.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys didn't come inside, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.32,0:18:25.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We saw it from outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.87,0:18:30.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, by going across this pathway around the spa...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.45,0:18:34.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Passing by the outside ventilation fan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.46,0:18:36.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And climbing over this fence...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.58,0:18:37.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.50,0:18:39.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can see it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.09,0:18:44.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.47,0:18:45.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just where did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.18,0:18:49.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This veranda is connected to a pathway outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.98,0:18:52.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.02,0:18:55.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, because this glass door wasn't locked...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.98,0:18:56.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.77,0:19:03.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before 11:00 last night when the outdoor spa closed,\Nif the culprit hid in the dark corner of this pathway...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.28,0:19:09.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After killing the old man who came early in the morning,\Nthey'd go through the pathway from this veranda...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.62,0:19:14.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And most likely mix in with the guests who were\Ndenied entrance and clamoring about outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.66,0:19:15.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.21,0:19:17.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, for starters...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.71,0:19:24.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why not pick out those who came to this laketop outdoor spa\Nalone, without telling anyone else, from the guests around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.92,0:19:26.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit might be one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.10,0:19:32.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And as such...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.64,0:19:36.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The ones who came to this outdoor spa by\Nthemselves without telling anyone are...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.52,0:19:43.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Curiously, only you three people who just happen to\Nhave connections to the deceased Tetsuyama Ganji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.07,0:19:47.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, most of the guests were with their families.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.78,0:19:51.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only ones staying in rooms by themselves\Nwere Tetsuyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and you three.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.33,0:19:52.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No one else.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.12,0:19:56.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, while you take out all of your personal belongings...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.08,0:20:01.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please tell me your whereabouts and actions at\Napproximately 5:00 AM, the estimated time of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.88,0:20:06.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's begin with the one who is said to play the heroine\Nin the movie from the script Tetsuyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} wrote...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.84,0:20:09.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Natori Mishio{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, you go first.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.55,0:20:11.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're getting at...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.55,0:20:15.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But all I have on me is this pouch with my make-up and a towel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.35,0:20:17.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My room key is at the front desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.73,0:20:22.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since we were told to turn it in to the front\Ndesk before coming to the outdoor spa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.19,0:20:25.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was just waking up at about 5:00 AM.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.44,0:20:28.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I came here at about 5:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.74,0:20:32.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard that we can soak in the hot\Nwater while watching the sunrise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.07,0:20:34.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, I like hot springs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.45,0:20:36.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.75,0:20:41.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was the relationship between you and\NTetsuyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} just that of actress and scriptwriter?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.46,0:20:42.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.38,0:20:43.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.88,0:20:47.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seemed as if you were being wooed by Tetsuyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.22,0:20:53.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are even rumors that you got the\Nheroine role by becoming the great sensei's lover!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.93,0:20:57.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got this role because of my expertise!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.14,0:21:02.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't associate me with you, someone who got chosen\Nas a candidate for the starring role by sucking up to sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.48,0:21:03.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Candidate"?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.81,0:21:05.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was decided that it'd be me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.23,0:21:07.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.07,0:21:09.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You, the lead actor, at about 5:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.84,0:21:13.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was sleeping about that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.20,0:21:15.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I came here for a morning bath just before 6:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.99,0:21:20.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My only belongings are a towel,\Nthese cigarettes, and my room key.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.58,0:21:24.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You didn't turn your room key in at the front desk?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.59,0:21:26.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Too much of a hassle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.71,0:21:29.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I also brought my key with me instead of turning it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.17,0:21:33.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, I only came to look for her\Nbecause she hadn't returned to her room yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.80,0:21:39.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why my belongings are my\Nroom key, my wallet, and my cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.23,0:21:41.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At about 5:00, I was watching TV in my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.52,0:21:44.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,TV at five?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.02,0:21:44.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're an early riser.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.23,0:21:45.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.48,0:21:48.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In fact I woke up a little after four.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.78,0:21:51.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At about 4:30, I went to the front desk for change.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.99,0:21:55.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was that change for buying canned coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.58,0:21:58.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're up early.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.95,0:22:00.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's only 4:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.04,0:22:02.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got a problem, runt?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.33,0:22:06.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We met in front of the vending machine around 4:30, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.75,0:22:08.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.84,0:22:10.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.05,0:22:17.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The manager Tanzawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} couldn't have hidden himself\Nhere for the entire night to ambush and murder Tetsuyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.72,0:22:19.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Murder?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.89,0:22:21.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So this wasn't an accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.68,0:22:22.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.23,0:22:24.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.48,0:22:27.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although we can't say anything for certain yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.94,0:22:31.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit must be one of those three.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.49,0:22:38.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit who murdered Tetsuyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.90,0:24:02.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, the culprit has to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.00,0:24:04.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This woman right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.25,0:24:09.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That person was completely absorbed in their role and forgot that...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.73,0:24:16.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The conclusive evidence is still hidden in their own pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.59,0:24:18.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The murderer is still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.00,0:24:21.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right in front of my eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.95,0:24:33.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.31,0:24:34.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ring
